### Criar Usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "João Silva",
    "email": "joao@example.com",
    "cpf": "123.456.789-00",
    "perfil": "ALUNO"
}

###

### Solicitar URL de Upload (Video Treino)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/treinos/upload-url?nomeArquivo=meu_treino_costas.mp4
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Iniciar Treino (Gerar Histórico)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/historico/iniciar
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuarioId": "uuid-do-usuario-aqui",
    "treinoId": "uuid-do-treino-aqui"
}

###

### Webhook AbacatePay (Pagamento Aprovado)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assinaturas/webhook/abacatepay
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuarioId": "uuid-do-usuario-aqui",
    "status": "PAID",
    "transactionId": "txn_abacate_12345"
}
